      "comment": "ZING MATILDA (1) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 0.8 lengths (19.76) behind Kilcoy Gem at this track. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Can find winning form. SEBON BOLT (2) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 3 lengths at Gawler in a handy 22.77 beating Todd's Luka. Fair draw can see a good run and goes well over this trip. Leading chance again. ZINFANDEL DASH (8) was fast into stride from box five to score two back (22.82) then jumped from the same draw last time but got further back when 3rd at this track (19.90). Expecting another good run.",
